node.text: We loove that avocado toast, too!

🥑 Rise and shine, everypawdy! Mami and I are twinning away and having avo-toast for brekkie. Although hers smells abit tastier, i still love my squashy crinkly toy. Happy midweek and remember to stay pawsitive!
